    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! This beauty has been my reliable companion and is in really solid shape\u2014it's clearly been well-cared for and is ready to hit the road with a new owner today. It drives super smoothly and is just perfect for anyone looking for a dependable, great-looking ride without the brand-new price tag. I'm honestly going to miss it, but I\u2019m excited for it to go to a great home!",
      "price": 34500.0,
