      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound C6 Z06 featuring the hand-assembled 7.0L LS7 V8, renowned for its titanium intake valves and 7,000 RPM redline. This platform utilizes a hydroformed aluminum chassis with a magnesium roof frame to optimize the power-to-weight ratio. The drivetrain consists of a rear-mounted Tremec TR6060 6-speed manual transaxle and a limited-slip differential, ensuring balanced weight distribution. The suspension maintains its factory-spec transverse composite leaf springs and monotube dampers, providing exceptional lateral grip. Recent maintenance includes a top-end inspection and a full synthetic oil service for the dry-sump system. This is a driver-focused machine with crisp throttle response and a rigid, high-performance architecture.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Mechanically sound. Clean interior. Title in hand. Serious buyers only.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
